enchances the aroma and keeps the beer from oxidation.','','','','','','TUANG DENGAN SUDUT YANG TEPAT','Menuangkan bir lebih dari sekadar mengeluarkan cairan ke dalam gelas. Bagian dari karakter bir adalah kepala atau lapisan busa. Metode penuangan yang benar memberi aroma dan menyimpan bir dari oksidasi.','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Prost Beer Page',0,''),(22,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','What Is Alster',0,'','WHAT IS','ALSTER ?','','','','','','APA ITU ','ALSTER ?','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(23,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','What Is Alster 1',0,'','TASTE','With the well-balanced taste of lemonade’s sweet and sour, Prost Alster is fruity at the first sip but you still can taste the beer within.','','','','','','RASA','Dengan rasa seimbang dari limun manis dan asam, Prost Alster adalah buah pada tegukan pertama namun Anda masih bisa mencicipi bir di dalamnya.','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(24,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','What Is Alster 2',0,'','FLAVOR','PROST ALSTER is the newest flavored beer for urban drinker which combines beer with 10% of real lemon juice.','','','','','','AROMA','PROST ALSTER adalah bir rasa terbaru untuk peminum perkotaan yang menggabungkan bir dengan 10% jus lemon asli.','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(25,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','What Is Alster 3',0,'','PHILOSOPHY','The philosophy behind our motto, Unleash Your Alster Ego, aims to unleash your confident inner-self to break free from the mundane. In short, Prost Alster lets you to be the person you really want to be.','','','','','','FILOSOFI','Filosofi di balik motto kami, Unleash Your Alster Ego, bertujuan untuk membebaskan batin percaya diri Anda untuk melepaskan diri dari hal-hal duniawi. Singkatnya, Prost Alster memungkinkan Anda menjadi orang yang benar-benar Anda inginkan.','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(26,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','What Is Alster 4',0,'','ORIGIN','The word \'Alster\' originally comes from a river in Northern Germany, which color resembles the color of this mixed drink.','','','','','','ASAL','Kata \'Alster\' awalnya berasal dari sungai di Jerman Utara, yang warnanya menyerupai warna minuman campuran ini.','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(27,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','Alster Video',0,'','Alster Video','','','','','','','','','','','',1,1,1,1,0,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(28,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,12,'','','Product Range',0,'','ALSTER CAN','330 ML','','2,9% Alcohol','','','','ALSTER KALENG','330 ML','','','',1,0,0,1,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Hidden','','Alster Beer Page',0,''),(29,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,3,'','','Past Events',0,'','PAST','EVENTS','<p>Missed the festivities? Don\'t worry, we got you covered.</p>','','','','','EVENT','SEBELUMNYA','','','',1,0,0,0,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Navbar','','Good Events',0,''),(30,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,6,'','','Good News',0,'','GOOD','NEWS','<p>Boost your mood with the good news!</p>','','','','','GOOD','NEWS','','','',1,0,0,0,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Navbar','','Good News',0,''),(31,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1,1,7,'','','Good Brewery',0,'','THE','BREWERY','<h4 class=\"home-news-quote\">Welcome to BIA BREWERY, home of the Good Beer. Established in 2015, the area spans more than 150,000 m2. It houses the most modern and innovative manufacturing facility, made by KRONES Germany.</h4>','','','','','THE','BREWERY','','','',1,0,0,0,1,1,1,1,'Super Admin','Navbar','','Good Brewery',0,''),(32,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,1